<qandaentry>
<question>
<para
>Ndizigcina phi iifayile zam ukuba ndifuna ukuvela ngqo kwi desktop?</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para
><filename class="directory"
>$<envar
>HOME</envar
>/Desktop</filename
>. Ungafuna ukuhlaziya eyakho ideskyop emva kokugcina iifayile zakho.</para>
</answer>
